{{about|the role of host at a public speaking event|other uses|Toastmaster (disambiguation)}}
{{multiple issues|
{{sections|date=June 2018}}
{{unfocused|date=June 2018}}
{{Globalize|2=USA|2name=the United States|date=June 2018}}
